OL,3,CDashcam footage appeal after boy dies
OL,4,Cin Lewisham car crash
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for dashcam
OL,7,Ffootage after a 16-year-old boy was
OL,8,Fkilled in a car crash in Lewisham.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to Manor Lane
OL,11,Flast Thursday and the teenager was
OL,12,Ftreated at the scene. He died in
OL,13,Fhospital a few days later.
OL,15,FHis family has been told are being
OL,16,Fsupported by specialist officers.
OL,18,FAn 18-year-old man was arrested at the
OL,19,Fscene on suspicion of dangerous
OL,20,Fdriving and drug driving. He has since
OL,21,Fbeen bailed pending further enquiries.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
